{"tid":1766271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇社民連 人民力量 熱狗呢個政黨","createTime":"2019-12-02T12:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T16:23:44.000Z","uid":193217,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a437663b7c3ba76beb500b2a6d08b84e22c0b1a7","tid":1766271,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"3個政黨最終都係搞到碎片化<br />\n目的為乜?<br />\n熱狗我一直都覺得佢係搞事黨<br />\n依家已經現晒形了<br />\n<br />\n毛哥既社民連依家應該由民陣召集人接班<br />\n而人民力量好似仲係無人接到班.以前係袁彌明<br />\n而熱狗.呢個真係今次選舉咩都睇到晒<br />\n擺明就係為左阻擊民主黨而存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06459a567412e0652993f185b36995379de25681","tid":1766271,"uid":193217,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:37:50.000Z","msg":"好明顯如果起民主路上.熱狗呢種真係唔會係同路人<br />\n顛9左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由14年佔中到今日都好似未醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486c2e0d62ba3d8ce6d085b72b3a18ae7f01badd","tid":1766271,"uid":116821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:38:56.000Z","msg":"快必慢必<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"e77082037b1a9427890fa634d2988a1711c6c858","tid":1766271,"uid":114665,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:39:22.000Z","msg":"其實分化有2班，<br />\n一班係屌柒人既熱狗<br />\n另一班係屌柒熱狗既人"},{"pid":"17a7f2256bc971e2679bfca9bca8d725bfe39e54","tid":1766271,"uid":230146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:41:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得慢必仲有啲睇頭，<br />\n呢三個黨不如直接玩完算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n私怨一大堆，<br />\n完全阻礙民主道路上既合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/